{"TopicId":168130,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"SSTO building helper mod?","CreatedByName":"FoxtrotUniform","CreatedById":182685,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T12:58:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"FoxtrotUniform","CreatedById":182685,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T12:58:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there any? Also piloting assist mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T19:34:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, many: I like \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E Build Aid, CorrectCOL. MechJeb\u2019s SmartA.S.S works as a lightweight attitude-hold module (though many consider the rest of the mod rather heavy). Other pilot aids I\u2019ve tried are extremely\u00A0complex\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T21:33:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u003Cs\u003Espaceplane\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0craft building aids I use and recommended are: \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Engineer Redux (mod)\u0022\u003EKER\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E building aid, Editor Extensions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are several pilot assist mods out there, usually pretty complex. None that I use often enough to recommend.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T22:12:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that I\u0027m in a real browser, let me add:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9507204508\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/17833-130-kerbal-engineer-redux-1130-2017-05-28/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3146495802\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/166546-131-rcs-build-aid-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9747945525\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/127378-131-editor-extensions-redux-released-with-selectroot-merge-stripsymmetry-nooffsetlimits/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3482536149\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/160231-13-correctcol-stock-aerodynamics-design-aid-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince many of these have abandoned versions and it\u0027s not always obvious when googling on names...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T22:42:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nModding question moved to the modding subforum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-02T23:50:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a video by Mark Thrimm\u00A0that explains how to do SSTOs. For piloting aids I use MechJeb and Pilot Assistant. (It\u0027s not updated to 1.3.1, but it works fine.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/8XI-DwXZm10?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}